title: The Busy Coder's Guide to Android Development v6.4
description:
The Busy Coder's Guide to Android Development

At over 3,300 pages, this book covers everything from introductory steps all the way to very advanced topics. More importantly, this book is continuously updated to reflect changes in Android itself, with new material being added every couple of months. Since you get updates via the Warescription, you are assured of having current Android programming information at your fingertips
